            this page will be used for my socials or my school stuff, just kinda me. and if im listening to anything itll show up here so
        </h2>
        <div class="lineline"></div>
        <h2>
            hey so if your here youll wanna hear about me, roxie. I like to think im pretty cool but theres not much evidence for that
            im pretty average by most accounts but to me I know theres a lot I can do and I hope I can show you that too, so please
            have fun (:
        </h2>
        <div class="lineline"></div>
        <h2>
            since you all know im almost done with school, ive got my final exam dates and so here they are:<br><br>

            Fri 10/05/2024 - 9:30 - 75 mins - combine science trillogy Biology P1H<br><br>

            Mon 13/05/2024 - 09:30 - 105 mins - English Literature Paper 1<br>
            Wed 15/05/2024 - 13:30 - 90 mins - Principle of Comp.sci<br>
            Thu 16/05/2024 - 09:30 - 90 mins - Mathamatics paper 1 Tier H<br>
            Fri 17/05/2024 - 09:30 - 75 mins - combined Science trillogy chemestry P!H<br><br>

            Mon 20/05/2024 - 09:30 - 135 mins - English lit Paper 2<br>
            Tue 21/05/2024 - 13:30 - 120 mins - Application comp. thinking<br>
