            Mon 10/06/2024 - 09:30 - 90 mins - Mathamatics Paper 3<br>
            Tue 11/06/2024 - 09:30 - 75 mins - combined science trillogy chemestry P2H<br>
            Fri 14/06/2024 - 13:30 - 75 mins - combined science trillogy Physicis P2H<br><br>

            Mon 17/06/2024 - 13:30 - 90 mins - Music written paper<br>
        </h2>
        <div class="lineline"></div>

        <div class="boxL" onmouseover="item_hover('I made a countdown using javascript, this was my first project in js','item0')" onmouseleave="item_hover('The coundown until i finnaly get to leave school (officially)','item0')">
            <a href="/projects/free">
                <h2 id="item0">The coundown until i finnaly get to leave school (officially)</h2>
            </a>    
        </div>

        <div class="lineline"></div>

        <h2>
            i think im gonna start writing some short storys so watch out for them here ^^
            {allPosts.map((post) => <BlogPost url={post.url} title={post.frontmatter.title} dates={post.frontmatter.pubDate} desc={post.frontmatter.desc} />)}
        </h2>

        <div class="lineline"></div>

        <h4>
            what are you planning to do next?
        </h4>
        <h2>
            i think im going to focus on me for a while, to feel more comfortable with myself but ill still be updating here, cause its fun
        </h2>

        <div class="lineline"></div>
        <h4>socials!</h4>
        <h2>
            <a href="">
                discord - roxcelic #0001
            </a>
        </h2>
        <h2>
            <a href="https://github.com/roxcelic">
                github - roxcelic
            </a>
        </h2>
        <h2>
